{"tid":1648563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由依家開始 我地要的係鼓勵 唔係失敗主義","createTime":"2019-10-12T09:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T10:17:24.000Z","uid":94771,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1efde9611bac8c8aab22f1c748cc08821b35bf77","tid":1648563,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:19:04.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗<br />\n<br />\n步入黑暗並不可怕，最緊要提起勇氣走返出來<br />\n<br />\n香港人不是鐵板一塊，創意力量和幻想會嚇你一跳<br />\n<br />\n不放棄，不割席，不指責<br />\n<br />\nBe,water. My,friend"},{"pid":"46bd44fe174f6633839a050b32f6b4428f1d429a","tid":1648563,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f56cda437282bd050f36633fe3da555489ee8f4d","tid":1648563,"uid":96664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"1506aa8e7ebbaa99fe7fbd74c7b39ffb72642cd5","tid":1648563,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062fc76e56f33eac9bd882a4de230bf61a5a88d5","tid":1648563,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca6a6b08cbf02a21b2d3f71bc31673a1b1d262b","tid":1648563,"uid":244520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"867ed3827aba5835188395830338c8b7f6f8aab2","tid":1648563,"uid":244520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88278bd0406d1a43805cb6ca1f2da4c248eff3c9","tid":1648563,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"fb轉<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解最近啲活動都咁少人<br />\n因為你地都唔撚識搞活動<br />\n<br />\n1. 一日十鳩幾個活動，就好似好撚豐富，但根本聚唔到人。<br />\n<br />\n2. 見撚到人哋宣傳緊啲活動，就咪撚同人哋撞時間； 原本聽日竟然同一時間有兩個尖沙咀遊行，整日程表嗰條友又覺得冇問題㗎喎，將兩個遊行放晒落日程表。(已update做一個 1500尖咀見)<br />\n<br />\n3. 成撚日諗住快閃，晏晝四點出post今晚18區開花，邊有可能宣傳得切。再加上好多人唔係全職抗爭，所以佢哋要時間去編排做自己私人嘅嘢，咁撚倉猝咪小人囉。<br />\n<br />\n4. 活動冇目的性，開花？即係做乜撚嘢呀？裝修又話唔好，拆鐵又話唔好，唱歌又話唔好，最尾咪成晚一班人鳩流流。<br />\n<br />\n5. 宣傳時間太短，連登唔係主流平台，文宣一定要靠Facebook IG連儂牆AirDrop發放出去，所以最少要有三日去做宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n6. 而家整文宣既，係冇人會做活動文宣，睇一睇文宣個Telegram group，10張有9張都係畫畫，得個靚字。你話文字定文宣會易宣傳啲。<br />\n<br />\n7. 我幾肯定，而家係有人鳩搞活動，目的打散人數。<br />\n<br />\n8. 同埋民陣去撚左邊度？又話會係咁申請遊行直至成功為止？<br />\n<br />\n再係咁樣鳩搞，只會狼來了，越嚟越冇人去啲活動。"},{"pid":"98292fc4b4e3de60c3877239b8295bb99477bc94","tid":1648563,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"勝負乃兵家常事<br />\n<br />\n勿氣餒"},{"pid":"4781ffdc5858a8cec61a36622d592ffdfb948425","tid":1648563,"uid":48061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"同意，雨傘就係咁輸。唔好再犯同一錯誤呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1780bb92c7137281e83f35589ff04de454be452","tid":1648563,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"推動BLIZZCON國際戰線要錢要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8cc64070f177a7ff85a0f154fe0fd1afd353d51e","tid":1648563,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"失敗係成功之母<br />\n唔好失敗完乜都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4e5a1b75696c0f7a51005912653cf7a7d29a5c","tid":1648563,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:08:09.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係！抗飛機都要講 我地係社運ai!"},{"pid":"da74fad615d350598db51ad17be80dc0ed43faf9","tid":1648563,"uid":244520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"啱 近排有唔少負面新聞 好容易習得無力感